Template-Plugin-DBM-Deep
========================

A thin Template Plugin around DBM::Deep objects, for easy access to
multi-level persistent sharable datastructures.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  DBM::Deep
  Template

